  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1556596,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, I think that's not sufficient,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1558515,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and so that was why we\nreally wanted to look at,"
