  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2962668,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, you know, one bar is\ndown here and one is up here"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2966296,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I definitely did not predict that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2968590,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there would be such a strong effect"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2970133,
    "dDurationMs": 4296,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from these, you know, reframing\nkind of interventions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2974429,
    "dDurationMs": 1043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That was a surprise to me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2975472,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think I totally agree."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2977683,
    "dDurationMs": 917,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I feel like it's so interesting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2978600,
    "dDurationMs": 3253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the way in which you have\nall of these correlations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2981853,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "entangled concepts in the\nmodel where, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2984648,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when it learns one thing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2986358,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it just somehow pulls along"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2987985,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "all of these other correlated\nconcepts and behaviors"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2990821,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and where is this coming from?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2991947,
    "dDurationMs": 1001,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, you know, fundamentally"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2992948,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's coming from this pre-training,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2994408,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's coming from the model has,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2995909,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, looked at all of\nthese documents on the internet,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2999037,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, stuff like this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3000288,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and really it's\ninternalized these ideas of,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3002541,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, what things should go together,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3004835,
    "dDurationMs": 1251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what things shouldn't go together,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3006086,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which behaviors are correlated,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3007796,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which behaviors aren't correlated."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3009464,
    "dDurationMs": 2419,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then when you, you know,\nyou try to pull one out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3011883,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and suddenly you have\nall of these other things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3013760,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you didn't intend\ncoming along with it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3015762,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in some sense that's great"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3017055,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because it means if you can\npull out the right behaviors,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3019307,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can get all of these\nother good behaviors."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3020809,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But it's also dangerous 'cause it means,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3022519,
    "dDurationMs": 1793,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, if you pull at something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3024312,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you thought was fine,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3025814,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but actually, you know, the\nmodel's understanding of it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3028358,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "had it be correlated with\nall these other bad things,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3030360,
    "dDurationMs": 1502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then suddenly you're in a lot of trouble."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3031862,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Does anyone have any final takeaways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3033739,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they might wanna share\nfor people who are interested"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3036033,
    "dDurationMs": 1668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in getting into safety research?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3037701,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Maybe Evan?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3039161,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I mean, I think that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3040454,
    "dDurationMs": 2043,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, we're very excited\nabout doing this sort of work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3042497,
    "dDurationMs": 3796,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We do a lot of this sort\nof work in Anthropic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3046293,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "really trying to understand"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3047753,
    "dDurationMs": 2752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how do we predict in advance what,"
